768
01:05:18.458 --> 01:05:22.083
We've been here for 24 hours,
he might have thought I'm in trouble.

769
01:05:24.542 --> 01:05:27.042
Your boyfriend drove
through the night

770
01:05:27.125 --> 01:05:30.583
