775
01:05:48.375 --> 01:05:49.750
Now wave.

776
01:05:53.958 --> 01:05:55.250
And smile.

777
01:05:59.042 --> 01:06:00.625
[boat motor hums]

778
01:06:02.792 --> 01:06:04.958
