down here guys.</i>

910
01:17:59.375 --> 01:18:00.708
<i>I see you, thank you.</i>

911
01:18:00.792 --> 01:18:01.875
<i>We're coming home now.</i>

912
01:18:07.667 --> 01:18:10.583
