awake at night,</i>

930
01:19:37.958 --> 01:19:41.667
<i>I feel like I can finally
put it behind me.</i>

931
01:19:46.333 --> 01:19:48.625
He gave me the courage to go on...

932
01:19:51.958 --> 01:19:53.125
With you.

933
01:19:57.000 --> 01:19:58.333
