935
01:20:07.375 --> 01:20:09.417
[romantic music]

936
01:20:13.250 --> 01:20:14.458
I love you.

937
01:20:15.917 --> 01:20:17.292
I love you too.

938
01:20:18.583 --> 01:20:19.750
Let's go home.

939
01:20:21.042 --> 01:20:22.250
Please.

940
01:20:28.458 --> 01:20:30.125
I'll start her up.

941
01:20:39.042 --> 01:20:40.333
[sighs]

942
01:20:52.500 --> 01:20:53.875
[sighs]

943
01:20:53.958 --> 01:20:55.083
[dramatic music]

944
01:20:55.167 --> 01:20:56.625
[choking]

945
01:20:57.458 --> 01:20:58.667
[choking]

946
01:21:00.042 --> 01:21:02.917
-This is for Jose!
-[choking]

947
01:21:03.000 --> 01:21:04.167
